column5: I just made an updated compilation of underwater pike strikes.  I hope you guys like it.
Very cool i didn’t have time to watch it all right now   Will finish tonight but I love the way once they commit, they’re all in on the attack and it sure shows why strong leaders are needed
Vicious strikes! Love how aggressive they can be at times and how timid at others!

In this video the baits were on a slow retrieve, they have more time to follow and analyze the bait.  When the baits are on a faster retrieve, they’re attacks are vicious. Thanks, I hope to capture some more after covid.  Do you still rep Mend-it?  I need that stuff for these swimbaits.  I can’t find that stuff anywhere in the GTA.
I do! Where do you usually shop at? They all have access to it!

I just called JB Fishing Depot and the guy said they’re sold out.  He’s not sure if he’ll order anymore because of covid. Al Flahertys is another shop but I don’t think they carry it. I also shop at Sail but I’ve never seen them there.
JB’s can definitely order them in! Let me see what I can do!
They'll be available from https://www.canadiantacklestore.com/ shortly! They just getting their shipment in and will get it up on their website soon!
Sweet footage. Do you use the waterworlf camera?
Awesome!  Thanks! Yes, I also use a gofish cam
Very cool, no wonder they call them "Gators"!
